detail.name: Android 18
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 3 cards from the top of your deck, then reveal up to 1 card with a cost of 5 or less and 《Android》 in its special traits and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: 人造人間18号
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のデッキの上から3枚を見て、コスト5以下の特徴《人造人間》を持つカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
